  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to KGlobalAccel</title>

    <para>
      The <application>KGlobalAccel</application> package contains a library
      that allows you to have global accelerators that are independent of
      the focused window.
    </para>

    &lfs75_checked;

